name: Stormeth the Rabbit
description: From the Chronicles of Rabbits in the Basque Country (Vol 2, Chap 5, Verse 11): Stormeth, colloquially known as "Stormy", Daughter of Snowfields Warmburrow. Enjoying breakfast in a lush Basque Country field, circa 2020. Photography: Jonathan. Hair & Makeup: Miss Softleap. Stylist: Stormeth opted for a "Birthday Suit" natural look.
